{"tid":1104702,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"投資大師警告：熊市或很快再臨","createTime":"2019-04-13T10:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T19:55:15.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b86a18878d3843f98a26d9fa88743d912c3623b1","tid":1104702,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190412/photo/bkn-20190412040109686-0412_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190412063549\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190412%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190412040109686-0412_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190412063549&h=be152a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投資者關注美企進入業績期，其中，摩根大通和富國銀行率先於周五放榜；至於下周發業績的企業包括花旗集團、貝萊德等。市場預期今年首季，標指企業盈利按年下跌4.3%，勢創自2016年來首次錄得跌幅；收入則料跌少於5%。<br />\n<br />\n數據方面，美國上周初請失業人數與1969年以來首次跌破20萬，顯示勞動力市場表現持續強勁。另外，3月PPI環比增長0.6%，超市場預期，創5個月最大漲幅。<br />\n<br />\n對於後市，美國投資大師、Leuthold Group首席投資策略員Jim Paulsen接受外媒訪問時表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">熊市或很快重臨。</span>他認為，應該增加對其他市場的投資，以對沖美股的風險。<br />\n<br />\nPaulsen表示︰「由現在起直至夏季，我們將會看到經濟是是好是壞...若股市沒有大冧，那麼到下半年則可以升得更高。」惟他亦表示，就算標準普爾500指數再升一成，但仍不能排除會出現衰退。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">他說︰「我們會回到股市過熱及下行壓力之中。」他認為，這種情況可能早在今年底或明年的某個時候再次出現。</span>"},{"pid":"0234ceeef580f612fc773ecad8cd64ab191322a1","tid":1104702,"uid":198008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"佢都認衣家係大牛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fa93d2136d356c60bd3682f4221334cf5e7fbb","tid":1104702,"uid":59461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:42:13.000Z","msg":".若股市沒有大冧，那麼到下半年則可以升得更高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢計漏左其實仲可能窄福上落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731d6219408241be5846bb997d6a76fd9730af5b","tid":1104702,"uid":76105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"如果市場沒有下降現象，代表上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0572891b462c61bcae401fab856908a52f1b0a","tid":1104702,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"拖到明年7月就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cfb53813d7869c2106dd3be937ea926e99a1fc","tid":1104702,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"若股市沒有大冧，那麼到下半年則可以升得更高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba445be23501d661d707f5e4df4c96b6fd9d85a8","tid":1104702,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76cfb53813d7869c2106dd3be937ea926e99a1fc","tid":1104702,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"若股市沒有大冧，那麼到下半年則可以升得更高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"佢冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a6fe410ea9a3cfbeab5a46db1fe44183e24e88","tid":1104702,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"事實係熊市之前一定係牛3"},{"pid":"598ad4fd54f1777e5311c445248350ec36859800","tid":1104702,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:16:52.000Z","msg":"龍一"},{"pid":"1ba5c39788c819b512c5f1bb1ca4f05e04af194a","tid":1104702,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:55:15.000Z","msg":"驚閪, 都未到周街股神, 仲有得玩"}]}